## Proposed Changes

### Core Gamification Logic

#### [NEW] [gamificationSlice.ts](file:///c:/DEV/ooskills-frontend/src/store/slices/gamificationSlice.ts)
- Redux slice with mock gamification state: `xp`, `level`, `levelTitle`, `xpForCurrentLevel`, `xpForNextLevel`, `streak`, `achievements[]`
- Level thresholds table (10 levels, progressive curve)
- Computed selectors: `selectLevelProgress` (0–100%), `selectCurrentLevel`, `selectStreak`

---

### Profile Avatar with XP Ring

#### [NEW] [LevelAvatar.tsx](file:///c:/DEV/ooskills-frontend/src/components/student/LevelAvatar.tsx)
- Reusable component wrapping any avatar (image or initials fallback)
- SVG circular progress ring around the avatar with gold stroke
- Small circular badge at bottom-right showing level number
- Props: `src`, `alt`, `name`, `size` (sm/md/lg), `level`, `progress` (0–1)
- Renders `rounded-full` avatar inside SVG viewBox with arc path

#### [MODIFY] [Header.tsx](file:///c:/DEV/ooskills-frontend/src/components/Header.tsx)
- Replace avatar render at lines 264–278 (desktop) and 360–374 (mobile) with `<LevelAvatar>`
- Import `useAppSelector` to read level/progress from gamification slice

#### [MODIFY] [StudentHeader.tsx](file:///c:/DEV/ooskills-frontend/src/components/student/StudentHeader.tsx)
- Replace avatar render at lines 201–215 with `<LevelAvatar>`

