#### [NEW] [LevelUpModal.tsx](file:///c:/DEV/ooskills-frontend/src/components/student/LevelUpModal.tsx)
- Full-screen animated modal shown on level-up (Framer Motion scale + fade + spring)
- Canvas-based confetti particles (gold + oxford colors, gravity + fade)
