- Plays level-up sound effect on open

#### [NEW] [XPGainToast.tsx](file:///c:/DEV/ooskills-frontend/src/components/student/XPGainToast.tsx)
- Floating "+50 XP" notification that appears at bottom-right
- Slide-up + fade-out animation with Framer Motion `AnimatePresence`
- Plays subtle XP chime sound

#### [NEW] [AchievementToast.tsx](file:///c:/DEV/ooskills-frontend/src/components/student/AchievementToast.tsx)
- Slide-in toast for newly unlocked achievements
- Shows achievement icon + title, auto-dismisses after 4s
- Achievement unlock sound plays on appear

#### [NEW] [useSoundEffects.ts](file:///c:/DEV/ooskills-frontend/src/hooks/useSoundEffects.ts)
- Custom hook providing `playLevelUp()`, `playAchievement()`, `playXPGain()` methods
- Reads mute preference from localStorage
- Preloads audio files for instant playback

#### [NEW] Sound assets in `public/sounds/`
- `level-up.mp3` — triumphant fanfare (~1s)
- `achievement.mp3` — satisfying unlock chime (~0.5s)
- `xp-gain.mp3` — subtle coin/sparkle sound (~0.3s)

> [!NOTE]
> Sound files will be small, royalty-free audio. We can generate placeholder beeps initially and replace with polished sounds later.

